object.script:
max = 0.00005 min = -0.01 Factor = 125
function onTick() Pitch = input.getNumber(1) Speed = input.getNumber(2)
if Speed>0 then x = Speed SpeedComp = -6.062*10^-8*x^3+9.313*10^-6*x^2-8.708*10^-5*x-0.0075 if SpeedComp > max then SpeedComp = max elseif SpeedComp < min then SpeedComp = min end else SpeedComp = 0 end
Output = (-Pitch/125) + SpeedComp output.setNumber(1, Output) end
